{
  "stem": "2118.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They helped some, but they too-- the money didn't come in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't-- it was not rich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was poor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I wouldn't say that there weren't rich people, even in the neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were rich people in Balut.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Some were very wealthy, but the-- the general population was not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The Jewish life was very rich.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We had at least, not to exaggerate, at least four or five daily Yiddish newspapers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In our house, we had a-- the-- the-- a Jewish newspaper every day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And on the weekend, the-- the Jewish newspaper for the weekend came out with a supplement like with pictures and things-- just like here, Sunday paper.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We also bought the Polish paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And since I could read Yiddish-- not perfect-- Polish was easier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So naturally, I had the Polish paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But I have no problem reading Jewish either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I used to-- we used to go-- I used to go to the library and get books.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I liked to read a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I spent a lot of time reading.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Going to the movies, was for mine age, the biggest entertainment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But there was a lot of other entertainments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were dance halls where the young people get together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There were all kind of organizations were by the dozens, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the [NON-ENGLISH] or the [NON-ENGLISH] or-- or the Zionist and-- and the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the biggest party was-- was the Bund.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And being in the neighborhood where I lived, most people supported the Bund.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The Bund was the socialist party of Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But the Jewish section was separate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So they had this big hall, and I used to go along with some of the friends of mine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we had a lot of fun there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We played games.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We learned songs.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
